text: Rogelio Famatid (born 9 December 1943) is a Filipino wrestler. He competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Filipino male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the Philippines Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Iloilo City
title: Rogelio Famatid
